SampleDescription.Description: mosaic: a ring X containing one copy of the material from Xp11.22 to Xp11.21 and two copies of the material from Xq11.1 to Xq21.2. The ring X was observed in 15 of 30 metaphase cells and 44.0% of nuclei from a PHA-stimulated culture, as well as 52.0% of nuclei from a direct preparation.
